  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel's restaurant serves up a daily American buffet breakfast full of tasty treats to set you up for the day.</p>
<p>The hotel's bed &amp; breakfast board basis gives you the opportunity to head out and try some of the fantastic local restaurants in Selva and its nearby towns. This is a great way to get a true taste of the traditional food and the atmosphere of the towns in the evening.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
