  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Val Gardena Active Programme partner accommodation</strong></p>
<p>Hotel Aaritz is an affiliate of the <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.valgardena-active.com/en/summer" target="_blank">Val Gardena Active</a> programme so you can join free or discounted activities every day of the week (activities are bookable and payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Hotel Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wellness area with a heated indoor pool, whirlpool, sauna, Turkish bath and relaxation area with comfortable loungers and views of the mountains</li>
<li>Pool towels are available free of charge</li>
<li>Massages and beauty treatments are payable locally</li>
<li>Fitness Room</li>
<li>Bar</li>
<li>Lounge</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking available</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
