  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>are around 24<span>m² </span> and sleep two people. They have a balcony and a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms </strong>are between 32-35<span>m² </span> and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are also available and have a shower stall.</p>
<p>Please request twin or double beds at the time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Mini fridge</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request for approx. €20 per day, payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €3 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
